OL,3,CRemembering the 327 Guernseymen who
OL,4,Clost their lives in the Battle of
OL,5,CCambrai
OL,7,FA battle which virtually wiped out a
OL,8,Fgeneration of Guernseymen has been
OL,9,Fcommemorated.
OL,11,FPeople gathered in both Guernsey and
OL,12,FFrance to remember the bravery and
OL,13,Fsacrifice of the Royal Guernsey Light
OL,14,FInfantry (RGLI) during World War One.
OL,16,FIt's the 107th anniversary of when
OL,17,FRGLI men lost their lives in the
OL,18,FBattle of Cambrai in 1917.
