OL,3,CRemembering the 327 Guernseymen who
OL,4,Clost their lives in the Battle of
OL,5,CCambrai
OL,7,FHowever, their losses were large, with
OL,8,F327 men from the regiment's total
OL,9,Fstrength of 1,000 killed, missing, or
OL,10,Flost.
OL,12,FThe RGLI only made their strategic
OL,13,Fwithdrawal, still under fire, when
OL,14,Fthey were ordered to by the high
OL,15,Fcommand.
OL,17,FThe high loss of life and inability to
OL,18,Ffind enough recruits from Guernsey
OL,19,Fmeant the RGLI would never just be
OL,20,Fmade up of Guernseymen again.
